{"tid":673453,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"馬浚偉畀七千蚊叫胡定欣騷六舊腹肌","createTime":"2018-05-22T00:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T05:22:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3b09294d9eae22909dd33550e92db90bf483fd7a","tid":673453,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T00:40:59.000Z","msg":"無綫新劇《宮心計2深宮計》今晚首播，一眾主演馬浚偉、胡定欣、馬國明、黃心穎、蕭正楠、劉心悠等齊集商場睇首播，引來大批市民圍觀，飾演夫婦的胡定欣與馬浚偉以情侶裝現身，胡定欣穿上白色超低V晚裝赴會，她表示期待觀眾對劇集的口碑及反應。<br />\n<br />\n而馬浚偉表示已叫定家人把屋企4部電視機全開煲劇以示支持，自己亦待完成工作後返家重溫谷收視：「雖然屋企冇裝計收視嘅電視盒子，但都叫做精神上支持，我係一個好盡責宣傳嘅演員。（擔唔擔心收視？）依家係網絡世界，收視計法同以前好唔同，所以完全冇壓力。」<br />\n<br />\n收視一定創高峰<br />\n至於同時忙於與胡定欣綵排舞台劇《偶然．徐志摩》的馬浚偉，大讚對方身型弗爆兼有六舊腹肌，更誇口謂：「我會運用自己監製同出品人嘅權力，希望加一場戲畀定欣騷腹肌。」胡定欣聞言即笑指會逐舊腹肌與對方計：「就收番一舊100蚊，總數6千6。」馬浚偉則豪氣表示畀夠7千蚊。<br />\n<br />\n對於被指性感登場，胡定欣解釋：「都唔性感，好自然，開心冇所謂啦！收視梗係想愈高愈好，我都係幸運星，今晚條裙又多星星，記得上年套《同盟》收視係全年冠軍，我有幸運星守護套劇集，希望呢套劇都係今年收視冠軍，同埋我今年都係得呢部劇。」<br />\n<br />\n馬浚偉亦自言以往也是收視福將，如今再加埋收視幸運星胡定欣，以及馬國明、黃心穎等猛將，相信收視一定創高峰。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180521/photo/bkn-20180521202852103-0521_00862_001_03b.jpg?20180522051842\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180521%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180521202852103-0521_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20180522051842&h=c9052b74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180521/bkn-20180521202852103-0521_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180521%2Fbkn-20180521202852103-0521_00862_001.html&d=Cf9YCzyxC9ID9a6tD1u72SwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f2145002\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180521/bkn-20180521202852103-0521_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ae7a374d56d78abcee0ea06549cb11a619bd7b7e","tid":673453,"uid":48658,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T00:57:30.000Z","msg":"一舊一百 總共六千六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a1a0e5421d09f910ef03f014fb46594331c73a","tid":673453,"uid":58140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T00:59:12.000Z","msg":"當我雞呀?七千蚊?<br />\n起碼都1萬啦"},{"pid":"fd5c9178b85eec81a043902994487ebf286ad5f7","tid":673453,"uid":102179,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"ae7a374d56d78abcee0ea06549cb11a619bd7b7e","tid":673453,"uid":48658,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T00:57:30.000Z","msg":"一舊一百 總共六千六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T01:04:41.000Z","msg":"六十幾舊腹肌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320a94182d2f63774c793958b7177a41d9dd3dab","tid":673453,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T01:25:04.000Z","msg":"垃圾劇"},{"pid":"0bdfe3aab52adf13c2016cd2252c030571ba2b7a","tid":673453,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd5c9178b85eec81a043902994487ebf286ad5f7","tid":673453,"uid":102179,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"ae7a374d56d78abcee0ea06549cb11a619bd7b7e","tid":673453,"uid":48658,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T00:57:30.000Z","msg":"一舊一百 總共六千六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T01:04:41.000Z","msg":"六十幾舊腹肌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T02:41:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd7910e1d444af3b6e33a6139b22b81298fc6d9","tid":673453,"uid":135767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"re